flowchart TD
    A[User Action: Add / Edit / Delete] --> B[Tulis ke Dexie lokal - optimistic]
    B --> C[Tandai sync_status = pending]
    C --> D[Masuk Sync Queue]
    D --> E{Online?}
    E -- Tidak --> F[Tunggu, retry saat reconnect]
    F --> E
    E -- Ya --> G[Push perubahan ke Supabase]
    G --> H{Sukses?}
    H -- Tidak --> I[Retry exponential backoff, status tetap pending]
    I --> G
    H -- Ya --> J[Tandai sync_status = synced, update updated_at]

    K[App Dibuka / Interval Berkala] --> L[Pull rows WHERE updated_at > last_synced_at]
    L --> M{deleted_at terisi?}
    M -- Ya --> N[Soft-delete / hapus versi lokal di Dexie]
    M -- Tidak --> O[Upsert ke Dexie]
    N --> P[UI update reaktif via Pinia]
    O --> P
    J --> P
